@baseUrl = http://localhost:5194

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### Get supported locations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/locations
Accept: application/json

###

### Run search - default locations
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/searches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locations": ["London", "Birmingham", "Leeds", "Manchester", "Bristol", "Edinburgh", "Cardiff", "Belfast"]
}

###

### Run search - custom locations
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/searches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locations": ["London", "Birmingham", "Leeds"],
  "areaOfLaw": "Conveyancing"
}

###

### Run search - single location
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/searches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locations": ["London"]
}

###

### Run search - includes unavailable location (Bradford)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/searches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locations": ["London", "Bradford", "Leeds"]
}

###
